      "text": "Here is how a sanctuary jurisdiction works: \n\n1. An illegal alien commits a crime, wounding (or worse) an American citizen;\n\n2. Local law enforcement arrests the illegal alien;\n\n3. ICE sends notice (called a “detainer”) to local authorities requesting they hold the CRIMINAL illegal alien so that ICE can retrieve and deport;\n\n4. RATHER than oblige and hold the criminal for an easy transfer and deportation, woke prosectors, mayors and governors ORDER the illegal alien be released onto the street. This of course endangers every American and compounds the difficulty for law enforcement everywhere. \n\nThese policies and their architects are dangerous, criminal, and must be stopped.",
      "text_resolved": "Here is how a sanctuary jurisdiction works: \n\n1. An illegal alien commits a crime, wounding (or worse) an American citizen;\n\n2. Local law enforcement arrests the illegal alien;\n\n3. ICE sends notice (called a “detainer”) to local authorities requesting they hold the CRIMINAL illegal alien so that ICE can retrieve and deport;\n\n4. RATHER than oblige and hold the criminal for an easy transfer and deportation, woke prosectors, mayors and governors ORDER the illegal alien be released onto the street. This of course endangers every American and compounds the difficulty for law enforcement everywhere. \n\nThese policies and their architects are dangerous, criminal, and must be stopped.",
